description:
Went to eat at a couple of pizza restaurants in Tokyo Japan where people and many publications have said has the BEST pizza in the world. That, of course, is a very very bold statement so I went to Da Isa where pizza cooked by Chef Yamamoto is called Damn near perfect by Time Out Magazine. Then it was off to Pizza Studio Tamaki for what I think is one of the best pizzas I have ever had.

Restaurants:
Pizzeria e Trattoria da ISA
1 Chome-28-9 Aobadai, Meguro City, Tokyo 153-0042, Japan

Pizza Studio Tamaki
1 Chome-24-6 Higashiazabu, Minato City, Tokyo 106-0044, Japan
